import React from 'react'
import {
    Table,
    Container
} from 'reactstrap'
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'



export default (props) => {


    return (

        <
        Container >
        <
        Table >
        <
        thead >
        <
        tr className = "text-capitalize align-middle text-center" >
        <
        th > Novos Usuarios < /th> <
        /tr> <
        /thead> <
        tbody >
        <
        tr >
        <
        td > Nome < /td> <
        td > Data < /td> <
        td > Participação < /td> <
        td > % < /td> <
        /tr> <
        /tbody>





        <
        /Table> <
        /Container>

    )

}
